      "value": 20,
      "unit": "%",
      "note": "跳级去啃进阶书：读得完，但慢到离谱（耗时 5 倍）。**不禁止，只是让你自己算这笔账。**",
      "_id": "read_no_prereq",
      "_anchor": "godot/scripts/SurvivorPerks.cs :: ReadingSpeed.MissingPrerequisiteMultiplier",
      "_icon": "",
      "sync": ""
    },
    {
